CREATE TABLE Departments (
    dept_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
    dept_name VARCHAR(50),
    manager_id INTEGER
); INSERT INTO Departments VALUES
(1, 'Human Resources', 1),
(2, 'Engineering', 2),
(3, 'Marketing', 3); CREATE TABLE Projects (
    project_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(100),
    dept_id INTEGER,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(12,2),
    FOREIGN KEY (dept_id) REFERENCES Departments(dept_id)
); INSERT INTO Projects VALUES
(1, 'Website Redesign', 3, '2023-01-15', '2023-06-30', 150000),
(2, 'AI Research', 2, '2022-09-01', '2023-09-01', 300000)
